{"tid":1454294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"它們是獵物，而我們是獵人","createTime":"2019-08-12T06:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T07:02:34.000Z","uid":231206,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4a2d7fecbc593ea45118b7c21805e36b4fc937bd","tid":1454294,"uid":231206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:54:34.000Z","msg":"一味埋頭祈禱  不會改變任何東西<br />\n可以改變現狀的是  戰鬥的覺悟<br />\n<br />\n踏著屍體前進<br />\n所有  嘲笑我們進擊意志的豬玀啊<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">家畜的安寧 虛偽的繁榮</span></span><br />\n我等寧願化為餓狼  身死也要奪回自由<br />\n<br />\n對被囚禁的屈辱  還以<span style=\"color: red;\">反擊的意志</span><br />\n面對高牆的一方  成為屠宰獵物的獵人<br />\n將噴發而出的殺意  披上吾身<br />\n以烈焰貫穿黃昏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n情緒低落 灰心時<br />\n請每日聽一百次紅蓮の弓矢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62169c1c25c8514bea6f13064fcc7af283b77523","tid":1454294,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:55:40.000Z","msg":"[替天行道]地下勇武行動將無可避免，請各位和理非手足做好不割席覺悟<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1454288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1454288</a>"},{"pid":"448154aff6946e0cd0659e12b0e86e63d57877a1","tid":1454294,"uid":41576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}